title: Judge refuses to throw out defamation suit against Cosby - Norwalk Citizen News
text:
In this Nov. 18, 2013 file photo, actor-comedian Bill Cosby poses for a portrait in New York. A federal judge in Massachusetts has refused to dismiss a defamation lawsuit brought against Cosby by three women who say he sexually abused them decades ago.
